{"iti57:0.1":"Itivuttaka 57 ","iti57:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti57:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti57:0.4":"Dutiyaasavasutta ","iti57:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti57:2.1":"“Tayome, bhikkhave, asava. ","iti57:2.2":"Katame tayo? ","iti57:2.3":"Kamasavo, bhavasavo, avijjasavo—","iti57:2.4":"ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo asava”ti. ","iti57:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti57:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti57:3.1":"“Yassa kamasavo khino, ","iti57:3.2":"avijja ca virajita; ","iti57:3.3":"Bhavasavo parikkhino, ","iti57:3.4":"vippamutto nirupadhi; ","iti57:3.5":"Dhareti antimam deham, ","iti57:3.6":"jetva maram savahinin”ti. ","iti57:4.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti57:4.2":"Atthamam. "}